# Java Multithreading & Async

## 禁止事项

- ❌ `new Thread(...).start()` — 裸线程，无法管控
- ❌ `Executors.newFixedThreadPool(...)` — 无界队列，OOM 风险
- ❌ `CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(...)` 不传 Executor — 隐式使用 `ForkJoinPool.commonPool()`
- ❌ 在 `@Transactional` 方法内直接调用 `@Async` 方法 — 事务不跨线程传播

## 正确做法

### 异步任务 (`@Async`)

```java
// ✅ 必须指定 bean 名称，使用自定义线程池
@Async("taskExecutor")
public CompletableFuture<Void> sendEmailAsync(String to, String token) {
    emailService.send(to, token);
    return CompletableFuture.completedFuture(null);
}

// ❌ 不指定线程池名称
@Async
public void doSomething() { ... }
```

### 并行 IO (`CompletableFuture`)

```java
// ✅ 显式传入自定义 Executor
CompletableFuture<List<Child>> childrenFuture =
    CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -> childRepo.findAll(), taskExecutor);

CompletableFuture<List<ShopItem>> itemsFuture =
    CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(() -> shopRepo.findAll(), taskExecutor);

CompletableFuture.allOf(childrenFuture, itemsFuture).join();
```

### 线程池配置

```java
@Bean("taskExecutor")
public ThreadPoolTaskExecutor taskExecutor() {
    ThreadPoolTaskExecutor executor = new ThreadPoolTaskExecutor();
    executor.setCorePoolSize(4);
    executor.setMaxPoolSize(20);
    executor.setQueueCapacity(100);
    executor.setThreadNamePrefix("sea-async-");
    executor.setRejectedExecutionHandler(new ThreadPoolExecutor.CallerRunsPolicy());
    executor.initialize();
    return executor;
}
```

### 共享状态

```java
// ✅
private final ConcurrentHashMap<String, Integer> rateLimitMap = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
private final AtomicInteger counter = new AtomicInteger(0);

// ❌ 无保护的 HashMap 并发读写
private final Map<String, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();
```

## 事务与异步的边界

```java
// ✅ 先提交事务，再触发异步
@Transactional
public void register(RegisterRequest req) {
    User user = userRepo.save(...);
    // 事务提交后 Spring 会调用下面的异步方法
    applicationEventPublisher.publishEvent(new UserRegisteredEvent(user));
}

// ❌ 事务内直接调用 @Async，事务无法传递到新线程
@Transactional
public void register(RegisterRequest req) {
    User user = userRepo.save(...);
    emailService.sendEmailAsync(user.getEmail(), token); // 事务内调用 @Async
}
```
